(My keyboard was all messed up, I couldn't type the letters "e","r", or "f"=
)

::Wolveritron::


    He headed towards the Ark, thinking about it. The =
Ark, where all the Autobots and Decepticons were held before the great war.=
 He had transformed to beast mode and was running as fast as his Wolverine =
legs could carry him.
    Upon reaching the site he scanned for nonmaximal =
signals. He attacked the closest one. (Not sure who's there, been away for =
a while, so the first one to respond to this is who I'll be fighting.)

::C=
yberShark::

    He received the message and was somewhat worried, if the A=
lliance did that, then what would the Predacons do?
    "Megatron, if it is=
 not too much trouble I would like to meet you on neutral ground, to discus=
s a truce, yesss."
(The "Yesss" was just for fun, "Before the Storm" was on=
 yesterday and Megatron basically used that line.)
